]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Local marketing is important for any business‚Äîwhether you‚Äôre a mom-and-pop with a storefront downtown or a large national franchise. You want to get seen and found by people looking for your products or services, which they‚Äôre often searching for locally. In fact, <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/local-seo-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nearly half</a> of all Google searches have local intent.</p>
<p>So, what are the best local marketing trends and strategies that will help you see success this year? Today, we‚Äôre sharing the top 14‚Äîas told by the experts!</p>
<h3>Table of contents</h3>
<ol>
