										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>When it comes to doctor review sites, you probably first think of major listings like Google, Healthgrades, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-most-used-chart.jpg" alt="chart of most used doctor review sites" width="936" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-72727 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-most-used-chart.jpg 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-most-used-chart-480x308.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.softwareadvice.com/resources/how-patients-use-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Data source</em></a></p>
<p>However, there are tons of other sites where potential patients may be discovering (or should be discovering!) your <a href="https://localiq.com/industries/healthcare/">healthcare business</a>&#8211;and leaving reviews. And finding the right ones can help you expand your healthcare business‚Äôs <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/get-found-online">online presence</a>. But with so many options, picking which sites to list your healthcare business on might feel a little overwhelming.</p>
<p>So, if you‚Äôre wondering ‚ÄúWhat is the best review site for doctors?‚Äù we‚Äôve got you covered with this complete list of doctor review sites. Plus, read on to learn key tips for keeping your healthcare business listings, well, healthy!</p>
<h3>Table of contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#what">What are doctor review sites?</a></li>
<li><a href="#why">Why are doctor review sites important for healthcare businesses?</a></li>
<li><a href="#sites">14 top doctor review sites</a></li>
<li><a href="#optimize">How to optimize your healthcare review listings</a></li>
</ul>
<div id="what"></div>
<h2><strong>What are doctor review sites?</strong></h2>
<p>Healthcare and doctor review sites are <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/03/01/business-directory-listings" target="_blank" rel="noopener">online business directories</a> that list your business information and reviews to make it easy for patients seeking a new provider. When you <a href="https://localiq.com/industries/healthcare/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">market your healthcare business</a> on doctor review sites, you can highlight key information like your:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/11/08/business-name-ideas" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Business name</a> and address</li>
<li>Phone number</li>
<li><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/12/19/best-healthcare-website-design">Healthcare website</a> link</li>
<li>Photos</li>
<li>Patient reviews</li>
<li>Practice specialties or specific service offerings</li>
<li><a href="https://localiq.com/scheduling-solutions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Appointment scheduling options</a></li>
<li>Accepted insurances</li>
<li>And more</li>
</ul>
<p>Essentially, healthcare listings and review sites can relay information from your website, highlight feedback from patients, and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/05/17/increase-online-presence" target="_blank" rel="noopener">increase your business‚Äôs online presence</a>.</p>
<div id="why"></div>
<h2><strong>Why doctor review sites matter for your healthcare business </strong></h2>
<p>When a potential patient finds your healthcare business on a doctor review site, they can get a complete picture of what your practice has to offer.</p>
<p>Plus, listing your business on these directories helps your practice <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/09/16/get-more-google-reviews">get more reviews</a>‚Äîwhich is crucial to the success of any healthcare business. Most people prefer to find their next healthcare provider through doctor review sites. In fact, <a href="https://www.softwareadvice.com/resources/how-patients-use-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">71%</a> of patients use online reviews as the first step to finding a doctor.</p>
<p>Consider these two additional stats on why listing your healthcare business on doctor review sites is so important:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.thedrum.com/news/2017/03/27/online-reviews-impact-purchasing-decisions-over-93-consumers-report-suggests" target="_blank" rel="noopener">93%</a> of people are influenced by information found on <a href="https://localiq.com/products/listings/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">business directory listings</a>.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.softwareadvice.com/resources/how-patients-use-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">90%</a> of patients use healthcare listing sites to evaluate physicians.</li>
</ul>
<p>Clearly, listing your healthcare business on doctor review sites and directories isn‚Äôt a ‚Äúnice to have‚Äù tactic, it‚Äôs a ‚Äúneed to have!‚Äù</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-stat-influenced-by-listings-sites.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - stat callout on number of people influenced by doctor review sites" width="936" height="353" class="aligncenter wp-image-72728 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-stat-influenced-by-listings-sites.jpg 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-stat-influenced-by-listings-sites-480x181.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="sites"></div>
<h2><strong>14 doctor review sites for healthcare businesses</strong></h2>
<p>Now you understand why healthcare listings and doctor review sites are so important. But which sites should you focus on? Here are the top doctor review sites for your healthcare business.</p>
<h3><strong>1. Vitals</strong></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.vitals.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vitals</a> specializes in <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/best-free-business-listing-sites/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">business listings</a> for popular practices like dentistry, OB-GYN, primary care, dermatology, psychiatrists, and optometry. It provides multiple ways for users to find your healthcare business since it supplies suggestions and searches by city, condition, specialty, procedure, or physician name.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-vital.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - vitals home page screenshot" width="900" height="490" class="aligncenter wp-image-72730 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-vital.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-vital-480x261.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<p>Vitals also makes it easy to claim your healthcare business‚Äôs profile with one simple form:</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-physician-profile.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - physician profile builder on vital example" width="483" height="638" class="aligncenter wp-image-72741 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-physician-profile.jpg 483w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-physician-profile-480x634.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 483px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>2. Healthgrades</strong></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.healthgrades.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Healthgrades</a> is a doctor review site that focuses more on each provider‚Äôs reputation rather than business information (though it does allow you to provide the basics like address and contact information). With this doctor review site, users can search for providers based on their specific needs or preferences.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-healthgrades-screenshot.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - healthgrades" width="900" height="440" class="aligncenter wp-image-72746 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-healthgrades-screenshot.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-healthgrades-screenshot-480x235.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>3. ZocDoc</strong></h3>
<p>Although <a href="https://www.softwareadvice.com/resources/how-patients-use-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">43%</a> of patients say they‚Äôd be willing to go out of their insurance network to see a provider with better reviews, insurance is still an important factor in the typical healthcare <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/09/19/customer-journey-map-templates" target="_blank" rel="noopener">customer‚Äôs journey</a>.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.zocdoc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ZocDoc</a> allows users to only look for practices that work with their carrier or plan. So, if you‚Äôre looking to highlight all the insurance plans your practice accepts, this doctor review site is perfect for your business.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-zoc-doc.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - zoc doc home page screenshot" width="900" height="510" class="aligncenter wp-image-72743 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-zoc-doc.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-zoc-doc-480x272.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>4. Yelp</strong></h3>
<p>A household name for local business listing sites is, of course, <a href="https://www.yelp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yelp</a>. When you <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-claim-a-business-on-yelp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">claim your Yelp business listing</a>, you‚Äôre opening more opportunities for local patients to find your practice. It has interactive map features and tons of ways for potential patients to refine their results to find you.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-yelp.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - yelp home page" width="900" height="454" class="aligncenter wp-image-72742 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-yelp.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-yelp-480x242.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>5. Google Business Profile</strong></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.google.com/business/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Business Profile</a> is a hub for healthcare businesses to land their spot in Google placements like Google Maps and Search. When you claim and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/06/10/create-google-my-business-account" target="_blank" rel="noopener">verify your Google Business Profile</a>, you‚Äôll have plenty of prompts and opportunities to create a robust listing for your healthcare business. You could try making <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/google-my-business-posts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Business Profile posts</a>, highlighting before and after photos, providing a robust business description, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-google-business-profile.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - google business profile" width="900" height="415" class="aligncenter wp-image-72732 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-google-business-profile.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-google-business-profile-480x221.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>6. RateMDs</strong></h3>
<p>If you‚Äôre not on <a href="https://www.ratemds.com/nh/portsmouth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RateMDs</a> yet, odds are, your competitors are! With over <a href="https://www.ratemds.com/nh/portsmouth/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1.7 million</a> providers already leveraging this doctor review site, listing your healthcare business on RateMDs is a no-brainer.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-rate-md.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - rate md home page screenshot" width="765" height="508" class="aligncenter wp-image-72731 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-rate-md.jpg 765w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-rate-md-480x319.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 765px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>7. Doctor.com</strong></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.doctor.com/search" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Doctor.com</a> is a healthcare listing site go-to for both patients and practitioners. For providers with <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/niche-markets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niche market</a> specialties, Doctor.com has extensive categories you can opt your business into. That way, patients can find exactly what you offer.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-doctor-dot-com.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - doctor.com home page screenshot" width="750" height="568" class="aligncenter wp-image-72740 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-doctor-dot-com.jpg 750w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-doctor-dot-com-480x364.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 750px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>8. Real Patient Ratings</strong></h3>
<p>The legitimacy of some reviews is a common <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2012/10/15/why-seo-is-harder-for-small-businesses" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEO challenge for businesses</a> in the healthcare industry. To combat this, <a href="https://www.realpatientratings.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Real Patient Ratings</a> verifies all its reviews before they‚Äôre approved to be on your healthcare business‚Äôs listing.</p>
<p>It also gives patients options to find solutions for long-term care as well as one-time procedures, since the doctor review site specializes in services such as cosmetic surgery.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-real-patient-ratings.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - real patient ratings" width="733" height="543" class="aligncenter wp-image-72739 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-real-patient-ratings.jpg 733w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-real-patient-ratings-480x356.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 733px, 100vw" /></p>
