<h3><strong>11. Apple Business Connect</strong></h3>
<p>Apple has a home base for healthcare businesses of all shapes and sizes known as <a href="https://businessconnect.apple.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Apple Business Connect</a>. The platform allows your business to get key information relayed across apps like Apple Maps and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-apple-business-connnect.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - apple business connect example" width="657" height="573" class="aligncenter wp-image-72736 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-apple-business-connnect.jpg 657w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-apple-business-connnect-480x419.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 657px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>12. Judy‚Äôs Book</strong></h3>
<p>We know at this point how important your patient ratings and reviews are to the overall health of your business‚Äôs <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/02/06/online-reputation-management" target="_blank" rel="noopener">online reputation management</a>! So, if you‚Äôre looking for a doctor review site built around <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/01/10/social-proof-guide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">social proof</a>, <a href="https://www.judysbook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Judy‚Äôs Book</a> is for you.</p>
<p>Judy‚Äôs Book offers plenty of healthcare categories you can list your business under, and the site requires location to be a part of the user‚Äôs search experience. This means that you‚Äôll be able to get more local patients through the door.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-judys-book.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - judys book example" width="640" height="574" class="aligncenter wp-image-72735 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-judys-book.jpg 640w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-judys-book-480x431.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 640px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>13. Waze</strong></h3>
<p>It‚Äôs one thing to get a patient to schedule an appointment with you, but it‚Äôs another to get them to show up for it, on time, in your office! <a href="https://www.waze.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Waze</a> pulls its information from Google Business Profile, so be sure your Google Business Profile is updated before you check to see how your business looks on Waze. However, you can always <a href="https://support.google.com/waze/answer/7101380?hl=en" target="_blank" rel="noopener">report a fix for a map issue</a> to ensure patients can find you in the easiest way possible.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-waze.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - waze" width="900" height="405" class="aligncenter wp-image-72734 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-waze.jpg 900w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-waze-480x216.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 900px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>14. CitySearch</strong></h3>
<p><a href="https://www.citysearch.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CitySearch</a> is a simple doctor review site where you can quickly list your business‚Äôs basic information, include additional details like any specialty practice areas, and sit back as the reviews for your healthcare business flow in.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-citysearch.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - citysearch listing screenshot" width="647" height="481" class="aligncenter wp-image-72733 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-citysearch.jpg 647w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-citysearch-480x357.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 647px, 100vw" /></p>
<div id="optimize"></div>
<h2><strong>4 ways to optimize your doctor review sites</strong></h2>
<p>Use these tips to optimize your healthcare business‚Äôs listings on all the doctor review sites we shared above:</p>
<h3><strong>1. Regularly check your listings for accuracy</strong></h3>
<p>Did you know that <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/reputation-management/10-online-reputation-stats-will-blow-your-mind-infographic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">50%</a> of business owners have seen incorrect information on their online listings? Not only that, but <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/best-free-business-listing-sites/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">68%</a> of consumers would stop working with a local business if they found incorrect information in online directories.</p>
<p><a href="https://localiq.com/blog/seo-mistakes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Avoid common SEO and listing mistakes</a> by regularly checking in on your doctor review site listings. To start, you could use an online tool, like the <a href="https://localiq.com/free-business-listings-grader/?cid=Web_WS_InContentTextLink_Freemium_Listings&amp;utm_source=wordstream&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=freemium" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LocaliQ Free Business Listings Grader</a>, to check all your listings in one quick sweep.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-localiq-listings-grader.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - localiq listings grader screenshot" width="808" height="650" class="aligncenter wp-image-72729 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-localiq-listings-grader.jpg 808w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-localiq-listings-grader-480x386.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 808px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>2. Ask for reviews (and respond to them)</strong></h3>
<p>The more reviews you have on your doctor review sites, the better. Of course, you can‚Äôt always ask at the end of every appointment, but you can encourage your patients to leave reviews through channels like <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/07/01/email-marketing-tips" target="_blank" rel="noopener">email marketing</a>, social media, and even <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/qr-code-marketing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">QR code marketing</a>.</p>
<p>Odds are, your patients will be happy to do so as patients who are asked to give feedback are up to <a href="https://www.patientpop.com/blog/ask-for-patient-reviews-in-person/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">three times</a> more likely to submit an online review. We cover more <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/16/how-to-ask-for-reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ways to ask for reviews</a> here.</p>
<p>Once your reviews start flowing in, be sure to respond to every review (both good and <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-deal-with-bad-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">bad reviews</a>). ¬†<a href="https://www.softwareadvice.com/resources/how-patients-use-online-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">66%</a> of people feel it‚Äôs ‚Äúvery‚Äù or ‚Äúmoderately important‚Äù for healthcare businesses to publicly respond to online reviews (without violating HIPAA, of course). Carving out time to regularly respond to reviews can make a big difference in your online reputation.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-responding-to-reviews.jpg" alt="doctor review sites - responding to negative reviews example" width="808" height="428" class="aligncenter wp-image-72747 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-responding-to-reviews.jpg 808w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-sites-responding-to-reviews-480x254.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 808px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://medicaljustice.com/how-to-respond-negative-patient-reviews/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">An example</a> of a healthcare business providing a thoughtful response to a negative review.¬†</em></p>
<h3><strong>3. Include a unique value proposition</strong></h3>
<p>Most doctor review sites will have an open section for you to fill out additional information about your business. Don‚Äôt be afraid to mention in your <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-write-a-business-description/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">business description</a> what makes your practice stand out. Including your <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2016/04/27/value-proposition-examples" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unique value propositions</a> can help you communicate what makes your practice unique and help you win over new patients.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-value-proposition-example.jpg" alt="doctor review site - example of unique value proposition in healthcare listing" width="883" height="507" class="aligncenter wp-image-72748 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-value-proposition-example.jpg 883w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-value-proposition-example-480x276.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 883px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><strong>4. Include photos when applicable</strong></h3>
<p>Speaking of capturing the attention of your audience, a picture is worth a thousand words when it comes to optimizing your doctor review site listings. Showcasing pictures of your office, your staff, or even your successful patients (with their consent), can help people put a face to your business‚Äôs name.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-photo-example.jpg" alt="doctor review site - example healthcare listing with photo" width="861" height="433" class="aligncenter wp-image-72749 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-photo-example.jpg 861w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/doctor-review-site-photo-example-480x241.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 861px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>The second listing here with a headshot image stands out more than the one above it.¬†</em></p>
