										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span>Unless you‚Äôve been living under a rock these past thirty or so years, you‚Äôve likely witnessed an incredible evolution in our use cases for technology in day-to-day life. There‚Äôs been a clear switch from landlines to wireless devices, printing out MapQuest directions to using a GPS, and from flipping through a phone book to doing a quick search.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-meme.png" alt="directory listings - meme about using mapquest" width="275" height="312" class="aligncenter wp-image-70608 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-meme.png 275w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-meme-264x300.png 264w" sizes="(max-width: 275px) 100vw, 275px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.pinterest.com/pin/554857616587165624/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<p><span>It‚Äôs no secret at this point that your business needs to be easily found online, and one of the best ways to do that is through directory listings. What are directory listings? We‚Äôre so glad you asked! In this post, we‚Äôre walking through:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span> Why directory listings are so important for getting found online.</span></li>
<li><span> The best directory listings for your business.</span></li>
<li><span>Quick tips you need to make your directory listings stand out.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span>Put your phone book down, unplug your landline, and let‚Äôs get to it! </span></p>
<h2><span>What are directory listings?</span></h2>
<p><span>Directories are like virtual Yellow Pages for businesses, but with even more information so that users seeking out products and services can easily find exactly what they&#8217;re looking for and make a decision as to the best provider for them.</span></p>
<p>Directory listings vary from platform to platform, but they may contain any of the following information about businesses:</p>
<ul>
<li>Name</li>
<li>Address</li>
<li>Phone number</li>
<li>Website</li>
<li>Photos</li>
<li><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/16/how-to-ask-for-reviews">Customer reviews</a></li>
<li>Posts</li>
<li>Special amenities</li>
<li>Menus</li>
<li>Booking/reservation options</li>
<li>More</li>
</ul>
<p>We&#8217;ll be covering a full list of the best directory listings later in this post, but some examples of business directories include Google, Facebook, Waze, Foursquare, Apple Maps, and more.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-logos.png" alt="directory listing logos" width="720" height="245" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-70649" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-logos.png 720w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-logos-480x163.png 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 720px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><span>Why your business needs directory listings</span></h3>
<p><span>Odds are, your customers are part of the<a href="https://datareportal.com/global-digital-overview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> 5.61 billion</a> people who use the internet. Your business needs online directory listings so you can be there when people are looking for your brand. </span></p>
<p><span>While that might feel like a given, here are a few more reasons why directory listings are so important for businesses:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span> </span><span><a href="https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/12-local-seo-stats-every-business-owner-and-marketer-should-know-in-2019-i/549079/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">46%</a> of all searches on Google are local, <a href="https://seoexpertbrad.com/local-seo-stats/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">88% </a>of which are looking to call or visit a business within 24 hours. Having your <a href="https://localiq.com/products/listings/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">directory listings</a> show up in these types of searches can help your business take advantage of this. </span></li>
<li><span> </span><span>The likelihood of a consumer purchasing a product or service increases by <a href="https://www.searchenginejournal.com/online-review-statistics/329701/#close" target="_blank" rel="noopener">270%</a> if a business has at least five online reviews. Directory listings help your business <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/16/how-to-ask-for-reviews" target="_blank" rel="noopener">secure more online reviews.</a></span></li>
<li><span> </span><span><a href="https://www.thedrum.com/news/2017/03/27/online-reviews-impact-purchasing-decisions-over-93-consumers-report-suggests" target="_blank" rel="noopener">93%</a> of people are influenced by information found on business directory listings. </span></li>
<li><span> </span><span><a href="https://localiq.com/blog/best-free-business-listing-sites/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">68%</a> of consumers would stop working with a local business if they found incorrect information in online directories. </span></li>
<li><span> </span><span>Directory listings have been <a href="https://econsultancy.com/82-percent-searchers-choose-familiar-brand-search/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">proven to increase awareness</a> of your brand‚Äìleading to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2014/08/14/increase-traffic-to-my-website" target="_blank" rel="noopener">more traffic to your website </a>down the line and an overall stronger <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/03/05/seo-strategy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SEO strategy.</a></span></li>
</ul>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-stat-callout.jpg" alt="directory listings - callout stat" width="698" height="428" class="aligncenter wp-image-70639 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-stat-callout.jpg 698w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-stat-callout-480x294.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 698px, 100vw" /></p>
<div class='et-box et-shadow'>
					<div class='et-box-content'><p><strong><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/1f4cd.png" alt="üìç" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Are your listings optimized for local search?</strong></p>
<p>Find out with our<strong> <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/free-business-listings-grader?cid=Web_WS_InContentTextLink_Freemium_Listings&amp;itm_source=wordstream&amp;itm_medium=blog&amp;itm_campaign=incontent" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Free Business Listings Grader</a>!</strong></p></div></div>
<h2><span>The best business directory listings</span></h2>
<p><span>There are likely a few directory listings you‚Äôre already familiar with, like Google Business Profile or Yelp. But there are tons of other more specific directories out there that will help your¬†<a href="https://localiq.com/blog/niche-markets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niche market </a>find you. Let‚Äôs go through the top business directories you may want to consider: </span></p>
<h3><span>1. Google Business Profile</span></h3>
<p><span>The name alone on this one might speak for itself, since <a href="https://www.google.com/business/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Business Profile</a> listings are often what pops up first as people are looking for your terms related to your business across Google Search and Maps. You&#8217;ll want to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/google-business-profile-updates-for-2022/#:~:text=1.%20Claim%20and%20verify%20your%20Business%20Profile" target="_blank" rel="noopener">claim and verify your Google Business Profile</a> before any other listing, and then be sure to <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/06/03/google-my-business-optimization">optimize it</a> so you can improve your local SEO and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/07/02/how-to-rank-higher-on-google-maps">rank higher on Google Maps</a>.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-google-business-profile.jpg" alt="directory listings - screenshots of google business profile pages" width="624" height="344" class="aligncenter wp-image-70609 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-google-business-profile.jpg 624w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/directory-listings-google-business-profile-480x265.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 624px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://searchengineland.com/google-business-now-lets-businesses-edit-listings-directly-search-281993" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a></em></p>
<p>Google Business Profile acts as a powerful local citation for your business. Find out how to build more <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/04/12/local-citations">local citations</a> here.</p>
<h3><span>2. Yelp</span></h3>
<p><span>Another popularity queen when it comes to directory listings, most businesses and consumers have heard of (and used) <a href="https://www.yelp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yelp</a>. In fact, Yelp has over <a href="https://findstack.com/online-review-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">244 million </a>cumulative reviews across its listings and almost <a href="https://review42.com/resources/online-reviews-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">100%</a> of Yelp‚Äôs visitors have made a purchase from a business listed on the site. </span></p>
<p><span>Clearly, you won‚Äôt want to sleep on the opportunity to have your business listed on Yelp. So check out our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2020/02/06/online-reputation-management">guide to reputation management</a> to learn more about how to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-claim-a-business-on-yelp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">claim your business on Yelp</a>.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-yelp.jpg" alt="directory listings - yelp homepage screenshot" width="624" height="389" class="aligncenter wp-image-70610 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-yelp.jpg 624w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-yelp-480x299.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 624px, 100vw" /></p>
<h3><span>3. Facebook</span></h3>
<p><span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook </a>has evolved into a one-stop shop for users to find business pages full of key information and reviews. Nearly<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/forbescommunicationscouncil/2018/04/27/do-people-really-look-at-facebook-reviews-heres-why-it-matters/?sh=3309412963b7" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> half </a>of all U.S. internet users have visited Facebook to check online reviews for a local business, and (calling all <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/06/02/b2b-marketing-strategies">B2B marketers</a>)<a href="https://blog.hootsuite.com/facebook-statistics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"> 50%</a> of B2B decision makers use Facebook for research when selecting a vendor. Learn <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/10/16/facebook-business-page">how to create the ultimate Facebook Business Page </a>here.</span></p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-facebook.jpg" alt="directory listings - facebook page recommendations example" width="624" height="343" class="aligncenter wp-image-70611 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-facebook.jpg 624w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/directory-listings-facebook-480x264.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 624px, 100vw" /></p>
