<p><span>Many people don‚Äôt realize <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a> can be just as valuable as Facebook when it comes to being used as an online directory. Between location-based search and tag features, plus the ability to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/how-to-link-instagram-to-facebook-business-page/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">link your Facebook Business Page to Instagram</a>, more and more users are tagging and searching for local businesses on this <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/01/11/most-popular-social-media-platforms">popular social media platform</a>.</span></p>
